{"tid":2023512,"cid":16,"subCid":0,"title":"將軍澳 ，寶琳附近有冇邊間茶餐廳係可以推介","createTime":"2020-05-19T05:11:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-20T02:24:42.000Z","uid":182730,"like":11,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"6224d9e36604aeed899313bd4f99dfa0db4dbd74","tid":2023512,"uid":182730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T05:11:11.000Z","msg":"我先推介慧安園商場<br />\n<br />\n呢個商場人流唔旺 ， 所以見到餐廳都唔係好旺場<br />\n呢個位之前轉過幾次手,<br />\n近排仔仔鍾意食揚州炒飯去幫襯<br />\n揚州炒飯幾次都keep到水準<br />\n飯粒分明， 唔會太油太濕太旱 ，啱啱好 <br />\n足料，份量多，夠味道<br />\n不過環境就麻麻地， 所以我同仔仔去多數嗌外賣拎走<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4034fe25762b6f2188068f02f022284c597f83f2","tid":2023512,"uid":98291,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T06:01:45.000Z","msg":"原來依轉咗做呢間嘢<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n當年嘅雅園<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8e49d74f4433cc76904cc5a09227caa27fe2551e","tid":2023512,"uid":277151,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T06:05:45.000Z","msg":"呢個商場冇咗間酒樓之後，都冇再去過囉"},{"pid":"796e7d9179df0229b55eb8bf378d3a6d12f82dcc","tid":2023512,"uid":249924,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T06:10:17.000Z","msg":"永興<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02c462240bc86b3f6013cbd552f01f75e6a3caf1","tid":2023512,"uid":182730,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4034fe25762b6f2188068f02f022284c597f83f2","tid":2023512,"uid":98291,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T06:01:45.000Z","msg":"原來依轉咗做呢間嘢<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n當年嘅雅園<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-19T06:49:11.000Z","msg":"雅苑最早響新都一期地下<br />\n之後先轉去彗安苑<br />\n最後變咗呢間<br />\n<br />\n雅苑響一期嗰時都仲未有禁煙<br />\n又開到凌晨兩三點<br />\n地鐵站對面位置一流， 食物質素又唔差<br />\n收工同啲朋友去食宵夜<br />\n又可以煲下煙<br />\n別有一番風味"},{"pid":"7d1ffbaf50816ce184be114c98b95af098e5bb2d",